dct_description_sm: United States. Central Intelligence Agency. Universal transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by shading and spot heights. "Imagery base: SPOT 5 multispectral imagery acquired July 2004." "Boundary representation is not necessarily authoritative."Map shows : Revised separation barrier, September 2007; Areas of control after the second redeployment under the Sharm el-Sheikh Memorandum, 21 March 2000. Verso: Indexes of Israeli settlement areas and Palestinian-populated area. "803313AI (G00197) 7-08.".
